<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA30">
<l>teḷitāka vuḷḷattaic cenniṟīi ñāṉat</l>
<l>teḷitāka naṉkuṇarvār cintai – yeḷitākat</l>
<l>tāynāṭu kaṉṟēpōṟ ṟaṇṭuḻā yāṉaṭikkē</l>
<l>pōynāṭik koḷḷum purintu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The thoughts of those who straighten [their] minds, so as to be clear,</l>
<l>[and] easily [and] well understand knowledge, like a calf</l>
<l>that easily finds [its] mother, go to the feet of him with cool tulsi</l>
<l>[and] desirously seek [them] out.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
